      DWR offers flood fighting instruction courses free to government
    agencies and non-profit organizations. We can provide a one day flood
    fight methods course at your site, or a two day, flood fight training
       for trainers course which includes techniques, leadership, and
          presentation style. Request Training Flood Fighting Photo

                        For more information contact
                           Flood Fight Specialist
                        Division of Flood Management
                        Department of Water Resources
                                916-574-1203

